<doc>
  <member name="INTERACTION_CONTEXT_CONFIGURATION">
    <summary>Defines the configuration of an <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/input_intcontext/interaction-context-portal">Interaction Context</a> object that enables, disables, or modifies the behavior of an interaction.</summary>
  </member>
  <member name="INTERACTION_CONTEXT_CONFIGURATION.interactionId">
    <summary>
      <para>One of the constants from <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/api/interactioncontext/ne-interactioncontext-interaction_id">INTERACTION_ID</a>.</para>
      <div>
        <b>Note</b>  INTERACTION_FLAG_NONE is not a valid value.</div>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="INTERACTION_CONTEXT_CONFIGURATION.enable">
    <summary>
      <para>The value of this property is a bitmask, which can be set to one or more of the values from <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/api/interactioncontext/ne-interactioncontext-interaction_configuration_flags">INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAGS</a>.</para>
      <para>This example shows the default setting for <b>INTERACTION_CONTEXT_CONFIGURATION</b>.</para>
      <code>#define INTERACTION_CONTEXT_CONFIGURATION_DEFAULT \ { \ {INTERACTION_ID_MANIPULATION, \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_TRANSLATION_X | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_TRANSLATION_Y | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_ROTATION | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_SCALING | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_TRANSLATION_INERTIA | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_ROTATION_INERTIA | \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_MANIPULATION_SCALING_INERTIA}, \ {INTERACTION_ID_TAP, \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_TAP}, \ {INTERACTION_ID_SECONDARY_TAP, \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_SECONDARY_TAP}, \ {INTERACTION_ID_HOLD, \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_HOLD}, \ {INTERACTION_ID_DRAG, \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_NONE}, \ {INTERACTION_ID_CROSS_SLIDE, \ INTERACTION_CONFIGURATION_FLAG_NONE} \ } \</code>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>